               <div type="nts">
                  <p n="drb1"> Cf. Nrr. &lt;a href='/books/dipdan/1324/dd_13240113001'&gt;90&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href='/books/dipdan/1325/dd_13250221001'&gt;170&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href='/books/dipdan/1325/dd_13250315002'&gt;174&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href='/books/dipdan/1325/dd_13250320001'&gt;178&lt;/a&gt; og &lt;a href='/books/dipdan/1325/dd_13250320002'&gt;179&lt;/a&gt;. </p>
